❶

8 M3,740 kg, 240 boxes

Within an hour of the donation announcement, the total jumped over $310,000. 2,715 people, 2,716 people, 2,717 people... the Wang Yi Bo fan club called it an "emergency" and decided that it would have to be shut down -- as if there were too much money to buy all that medical supplies.

It was the evening of January 23rd. Three days ago, the Wang Yi Bo Administration was debating whether to donate something to Wuhan. That night, Zhong Nanshan gave an interview to COVID-19, which confirmed the existence of human to human transmission. Some offered to donate, but they had yet to see any charity raise money publicly. So they decided to raise their own funds, by the club to buy supplies sent to Wuhan.

After the fund raising, bad news came, in advance of good contact with the mask manufacturers told the Club, all inventory was requisitioned, they ordered 100,000 masks to go up in smoke. The Management Group exploded in the pot, the hands of 310,000 as if hot potato, how to spend out? A fan suggested we donate the money to the Red Cross. The club management quietly and firmly refused to donate, the donation notice said to donate materials, we must do.

There were 18 people in the group, divided into two groups. Because of the shortage, one group has 16 people to manage the materials separately, and the other group is responsible for connecting the hospital and logistics, both at the same time. From New Year's Eve to the second day, everyone updates the news every day. While abroad, Iris made dozens of phone calls, searched through the wholesale procurement platform of the medical manufacturers, but always at three or four in the morning to go to sleep disappointed. Dozens of manufacturers, some of the inventory has been requisitioned, some have been on vacation, and some products do not meet hospital standards.

On the 24th, Iris found a new clue among her fans. A fan offered to hook up with a neighbor who works for 3M. Iris contacted the 3M distributor in Wuhan, but was told the masks had been requisitioned. Through 3M introduction, Iris found two factories in Xiamen and Shandong.

The boss took out the purchase contract, Iris and quietly double-checked, and added four additional requirements: Manufacturers to provide a clear time to time delivery, procurement costs details, copies of the identity card of the legal representative and business license. Factory inventory is not enough, the boss temporary recall staff, also called relatives and friends, more than 30 people in the New Year's Day overtime.

In the end, the Xiamen manufacturer provided 500 face masks and 7,000 pairs of replacement filters, while the Shandong manufacturer provided 200 epidemic prevention clothing and 200 pairs of protective eye masks.

At the same time, Jing Jing was already asking for help from the Charities Aid Foundation, which she knew well. In 2019, Wang Yi Bo became a charity ambassador for the Chinese Children's charity, and the staff of the charity took the initiative to find supporters to donate money to their charity projects. In more than six months, the club has raised more than $300,000 for its projects.

Children's charity staff told Jing Jing, micro public welfare and the Red Cross Society has cooperation, the support society only to the Red Cross donation, from the Red Cross to contact materials, and distribution to Wuhan hospitals. But when the club contacted the hospital, they were told by a hospital doctor that there would be a delay. The Booster Club is determined to donate directly to the hospital.

After that, the Children's charity will be introduced to the Wuhan Tongji Hospital to Jing Jing. Tongji Hospital replied, thank you for the materials, but the courier has been unable to enter. Quietly call to ask Shunfeng, JD.com, in the logistics companies public number backstage question, materials can enter Wuhan? The answer is no.

On the 25th, China Post, SF & F, Jd.com and other 10 logistics enterprises announced that they will open green passages for relief supplies from Wuhan across the country, but priority will be given to public welfare institutions, medical institutions, enterprises and institutions, individual donations are not accepted at this time. On the same day, Jing Jing saw Xiaomi's micro blog: in the early morning of January 24, Xiaomi donated medical supplies into Wuhan. Quietly think, millet can go in, then we can also go in with millet? She opened her address book and found a former Xiaomi Co worker, Wang Yi Bo, a REDMI spokesperson, who had been invited to the club's launch. Xiaomi quickly agreed, and the next morning helped connect a local truck with JD.com logistics, promising to ship the goods free of charge from Xiamen to Wuhan Tongji Hospital.

At 12:00 noon on the 26th, 8 cubic meters, 740 kilograms, 240 boxes and 280,000 worth of materials will depart from Xiamen on time for Wuhan.

Four days later, the supplies arrived in Wuhan, and after that, they were never signed for. Quietly asked the logistics side, replied: Special Period, the speed is slow. Asked Tongji Hospital Wechat, has not been responded to.

It wasn't until Jan. 31, when the official Weibo Account of the World Wide Web,@Wang Yi Bo Fan Club, quietly opened the picture and saw the cardboard boxes stacked neatly in front of the hospital, each box bears the logo: "together, fight against the virus! Refuel Wuhan, Hubei! This batch of materials donated by Wang Yibo Support Club. "

That's when she finally confirmed that they had succeeded.

❷

Transparency is the rule

The accumulated energy of rice circles was released in Wuhan epidemic. Not Entirely. Xiao's fans have donated 2.56 million yuan. Wang Yuan fans joined forces with Bo to raise 400,000 yuan, and 200,000 masks and 150,000 medical gloves have been put in place. Yan Xujia support group raised 200,000 yuan and donated 200,000 masks, 140 ultraviolet disinfection vehicles and 280 lamps to Wuhan. The AVUNGA support group even donated four molecular sieve oxygen generators and seven pulse monitors.

These spectacular figures come after a difficult time for the club's supporters. In a shopping spree, dozens of members came from various support groups. V (Singer)'s Tata pulled a list of medical supplies from a Chinese medical network, and Wang Junkai's support group MEIFA launched a fan hair circle of friends to a list of manufacturers returning to work during the Spring Festival.

He Luo Luo and Yan Xu Jia CP support the small z contact 30 or 40 medical equipment factory, finally contact a mask inventory, the boss asked for 5,4 times higher than the market price. Little Z told the manufacturer that she was going to donate to Wuhan. The boss, whether you donate or not, five dollars a piece, no counter-offer. Some manufacturers delay to mask quality inspection books, small Z from the evening until the next day at 3 pm, finally found that the mask is not suitable for medical use.

Zhai Xiaowen Back Club Management Apple contacted a hospital supplier, but the other side refused to platform transactions, insisted on wechat remittance, apple worried about being deceived, had to give up.

All of the club's results and processes are clearly visible on social media. Wang Yuan Fans United Support Bo published financial details, the smallest amount of income is 0.12 yuan, from the fans into alipay. V (Singer) announced the arrival times of the supplies at each hospital, with the latest arriving at Wuhan University People's Hospital at 19:11 on January 26.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
V (Singer) , what's the ETA on all the hospitals

Transparency is the rule in the restaurant business. As soon as the accounts are not released in a timely manner, or the way they are audited is unclear, questions arise: are managers going to buy a House with a sea view? Seaview house is a popular metaphor in the restaurant scene -- as a result of the 2015 general election campaign initiated by the Mayu Watanabe Foundation, the foundation was later found to be corrupt, amounting to more than $1.5 million. There are also rumours that the club's management used the money to buy a sea view house.

V (Singer)'s management of Tata Bar, for example: This is equivalent to a plaque hanging in the gate, all out of the interests of idols, all out of the interests of fans. On the other hand, Authoritarian Club management can be dismissed by fans at any time. A Fan club manager interviewed said that her previous administration had had an altercation with a fan and kicked him out of the official fan base, but kicked him out because of a personal grudge, it was banned by the group's "group rules. " Fans stormed the club: You can't think I'm the law! Soon, the manager resigned under fire.

It's not easy to be a fan-happy club manager. An undergraduate at one of China's best business schools, apple has yet to graduate with a master's degree before being offered a job at an internet giant. In December 2019, apple ran for office, and the first step in the campaign was to send in a résumé.

She pulled up her résumé and turned the internship column into a fan page. Apple has had nearly 10 internships as an internet company, but the star-gazing experience is no less impressive. She started to follow the stars in 2008, just to Zhai Xiaowen station opened two, one used in the game to play, the other is mainly after the debut to play money and support.

Resume approval, followed by a month of internship, during which she completed an independent media assistance. In her internship report, she solemnly wrote: My abilities match my management position.

At the end of the internship period, fans voted to decide who would be the final manager. The first round of voting took place in a group of senators made up of booster groups and powder-scattering groups, and the other candidate she was running against won. Then there was a group discussion. It wasn't public enough. If you want to vote, you have to vote.

In the afternoon, the club announced on its official Weibo account that as long as you provide a record of how much money you have raised and prove that you are Zhai Xiaowen's only fan, you can participate in the club's general election. Soon, more than 200 fans poured in. That night, the referendum began. First Release the candidate's internship report, and then move on to the second phase: the defense.

"How to regulate the relationship between the official fan club and the non-governmental Fan Organization? "

"The authorities are not the full leader, but they should help civil society organizations. "

"How has your previous life or stargazing helped you in your management role? "

"I studied marketing, and I know how to sell. "

"How do you think you can build trust in the club? "

"The first is to do every little thing well, the second is to take advice and communicate more with fans, and the third is to be as open and transparent as possible in financial matters. "

After the vote, apple was elected with more than the required two thirds of the vote.

After taking office, in order to financial clarity, apple specially changed a double card double-stay mobile phone, with the new phone number to register a club dedicated alipay account. Earlier this year, Zhai Xiaowen appeared on the cover of a fashion magazine's electronic magazine. Fans raised money for the event, and Apple's alipay account was flooded with more than 2 million yuan that month.

On the night of January 19th, apple made a live audio broadcast to all of its fans. She first reviewed this period of time the work of the club, told everyone: Must Buy Electronic Tomorrow! Then he invited the heads of various official organizations to join him in the interview, much like a live broadcast in which the question most frequently asked by fans was: What is the focus of the work after the club?

Apple replied that the next to return to the day-to-day data control review and anti-black purification, but also to do a good job in Shanghai concert support. Little did she know that the concert would be postponed because of the epidemic, and the club's next step was to donate 52,800 yuan and 1,000 pairs of goggles to Wuhan.

"It's a culture that carries with it

Everyone in the circle."

Once upon a time, the public's impression of Fan support was "Pai Mian" . For Wang Junkai's 18th birthday in 2017, fans staged a "sea, land and air" campaign to claim 18 endangered sea animals, buy 5,000 screens worldwide, and buy 18 stars in the 60th parallel, it's spelled "WJK. ". Should help out of the circle, but also bring controversy, A PASSER-BY EVALUATION: Why waste money on this?

There's a difference between doing good, and the public understands and supports it. Wuhan epidemic came, Douban several groups began to move the donation reports of various support clubs, netizens commented on the following posts: Kua Xx, XX is the most donated bar, XX is not donated.

"It's a culture that has everyone in the community, whether it's management or the average fan, thinking I'm a Groupie and I have to do it, " apple said.

On New Year's Eve, "celebrity girl fund-raising" hit the search engine. Wuhan Epidemic micro-public Welfare donations list, the top 50 are all the supporters of the club. The marketing number of the launch of the star-chasing Girl Neat praise: "With the heart of the hot star, but also with the most blood-hearted public welfare" , "too to love beans to win. Apple feels inspired: It's time to show the keyboard guys who look down their noses at starstruck girls.

The fans are worried. They're calling for backup. Why aren't they doing it? Also on New Year's Eve, Z  saw a donation announcement from another club, but by this time, she hadn't found the supplies. "Why can't I find it anywhere else? It must be because I'm not trying hard enough. "

At three or four o'clock in the morning she went to sleep, and woke up half an hour later, out of nowhere. First thing she does when she wakes up, she touches her phone to see if any of the manufacturers respond. Later, the small Z strategy is "donation donation donation to catch both hands, " the first donation, "to the fans to be assured" , can not let fans see other countries have donated, their own but no action.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
By February 4,18:30, Wuhan Epidemic micro-public Welfare donations list

Wang Yuan's fans have joined forces to support Bo's donation announcement. "Fan follows idol, " the popular retweet said. "In every difficult time, Wang Yuan's fans have joined hands with everyone. This love and responsibility from Wang Yuan is always the same. ". The idol is not present, but is mentioned repeatedly in the process of fans doing charity work. Fans believe that public welfare can help the cause of idols.

Charities are also learning to harness the power of their fans. In 2016, Wang Junkai's national local station alliance teamed up with a Student Aid Program from the China Siyuan Project Poverty Alleviation Foundation, which at the time was not well known to the Fan community. Four years later, the project's microblog is interacting with several sites a day, from Adou and actors to table tennis players and TV characters, with an estimated total of several hundred followers.

Within six hours of Cai's announcement that he was going to Danzhou to conduct poverty alleviation research, fans had broken the link to buy duck eggs, a local specialty, and 4,000 cases were sold out of stock. It was a positive signal to the authorities that Cai Xukun was standing on the side street of 82 King Street station.

❹

Forklifts and Barbecue Buns

January 29 night, Vulcan Mountain, Raytheon Mountain hospital construction live broadcast online. The logic of the rice bowl is starting to seep through here. The small yellow excavators on the construction site are called "Xiao Huang" , the small blue excavators are called "Xiao Lan" , the small forklifts are called "fork sauce" , the small forklifts are called "shovel sauce" , the concrete mixer are called "vomit mud sauce" .

Xiaoforklift's Weibo chat has 48,000 followers and was once the top of the fan chat list. Its fans are called "barbecued pork buns" . Someone posted in the super words: whose fans are you originally? More than 800 replies, the most liked answer is "Bo Jun Yi Xiao" , followed by "de Yun girl. ".

Fans personified the forklift into a cartoon, and supervision of the live screen in the forklift separately cut out, made into a forklift "straight shot. ". Control Evaluation Template was born: top-class flow small forklift, site baby forklift, site the most beautiful small forklift. The comments were scrolled across the screen below the marketing number and between the live webcasting session. An account called "forked sauce data station" has created a tutorial on how to vote for forklift truck on CCTV's live help list. "If you don't vote and I don't vote, when will x come out? "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The power list of live broadcast of the construction of Huoshenshan and Raytheon Mountain hospitals

CP Fan Z was one of ten million viewers who tuned in to the live broadcast of the forklift. On New Year's Eve afternoon, Z  finally found a shipment of masks, 2,300 n95s. She was gonNA give it directly to the hospital, but the phones were busy. Once the fundraising is complete, the club's first priority is to show the fans what they are spending. At that time, there were not many public welfare organizations that openly initiated donation. The Wuhan Red Cross Society was the largest one among them, and it had official certification. Small Z donated supplies to the Wuhan Red Cross.

Soon after the donation, small Z saw the Red Cross public accounts, "do a mess" , was exposed backlog mask not issued, CCTV live broadcast also people away from the reporter. "My blood pressure is going up, " she said in an interview, emphasizing her anger.

Every morning at 2:00 or 3:00 a.m. , Z enters the studio. She watched the forklifts and the workers laying the foundations, but more often she watched the bombs: some called the construction equipment "Wu Sangui, " others said, "the Shanghai supervisor has come to relieve work, " and many people accompanied her every time.

She didn't want to see "the negative news. " Forklift truck looked happy, and she felt good about herself. Half an hour later, the girl turned off the air and fell asleep.
